    <item>
      <title>莫桑比克抗议者封锁通往南非的主要道路</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/mozambican-protesters-blockade-main-road-link-with-south-africa</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据运营该路线的跨非洲特许经营公司称，周一，莫桑比克边境城镇雷萨诺加西亚的抗议者控制了多辆卡车，并用它们封锁了通往邻国南非的主要公路。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/mozambican-protesters-blockade-main-road-link-with-south-africa</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 14:49:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>最高法院将在选举后权衡基于种族的投票路线</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/supreme-court-will-rule-on-use-of-race-in-drawing-voting-lines</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最高法院将受理有关重新划分选区种族问题的新冲突，并同意听取有关路易斯安那州国会选举地图上新增一个黑人占多数的选区的辩论。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/supreme-court-will-rule-on-use-of-race-in-drawing-voting-lines</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 14:37:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>匈牙利议会投票通过法令延长奥尔班任期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/hungarian-parliament-votes-to-extend-orban-s-rule-by-decree</link>
      <description><![CDATA[匈牙利议会批准总理维克托·奥尔班将其法令统治期限再延长六个月，继续维持权力集中，这使得布达佩斯走上了与欧盟发生冲突的道路。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/hungarian-parliament-votes-to-extend-orban-s-rule-by-decree</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 14:35:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
